{"tid":1410151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過增加傳教士一職","createTime":"2019-08-05T00:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T01:04:05.000Z","uid":82536,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b20f818547699d81ab7a15430ce5ac56087073","tid":1410151,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"我明白 藍絲既思維同一般人係唔一樣<br />\n只睇cctvb 假消息 就以為自己知曬所有野<br />\n都唔識用腦思考 <br />\n無論身邊仔女點努力講解說服 都唔及班藍絲朋友既一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中意信任d 陌生人 多過自己仔女<br />\n或者正正可以利用呢點<br />\n用傳教士方式 去感化/教育佢地<br />\n<br />\n好似今日咁 好多藍絲阿叔激動咁鬧阻住番工<br />\n等佢鬧到差唔多完既時候 <br />\n傳教士（可能兩個女仔）走去（扮）關心佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁激動小心身體啊 <br />\n其實你知唔知佢地點解要咁做啊？<br />\n<br />\n佢講完 你再問得深入d <br />\n多數藍絲其實都唔識 問多兩句就答你唔到<br />\n但佢等緊車 周圍又多人 想走 想逃避問題都走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後你就可以開始傳教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳教士要有既技能：無害樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> EQ 高 已準備好多片段同圖 自發聖光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36958a8dce9dada20f521d8121c2202b825428eb","tid":1410151,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:48:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ced3bfe57e87df81950b9633e4ba62326c484723","tid":1410151,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c94fa9f94b09ed7a018ddd25ae538e48a063b79b","tid":1410151,"uid":221055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:49:04.000Z","msg":"呢個位置適合銀髮族/叔叔阿姨級嘅，後生講佢地都係唔聽架啦"},{"pid":"3e79dae88f4be18477b75edc721d705ede6390f8","tid":1410151,"uid":82536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c94fa9f94b